#: ../../docs/gentle_gis_introduction/introducing_gis.rst:7
msgid "Understanding what GIS is and what it can be used for."
msgstr "GISとは何か、何ができるのかを理解する。"

#: ../../docs/gentle_gis_introduction/introducing_gis.rst:9
msgid "Keywords:"
msgstr "キーワード："

#: ../../docs/gentle_gis_introduction/introducing_gis.rst:9
msgid "GIS, Computer, Maps, Data, Information System, Spatial, Analysis"
